 *
 * On native_sim there's no ADC controller wired by default; the
 * alp-adc0 alias resolves to a NULL spec and alp_adc_open returns
 * NULL with last_error = ALP_ERR_NOT_READY.  The example exits
 * after printing the diagnostic so the console harness can assert
 * the path runs.
